cohortName: Malignant tumor of prostate referent incident cohort
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (4163261) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: Malignant tumor of prostate referent prevalent cohort
logicDescription: Persons with condition occurrence of referent concept (4163261) or descendants, for the first time in the person's history, with at least 365 days of prior continuous observation. Persons exit cohort at the end of the observation period.

cohortName: Malignant tumor of prostate excluding secondary cancers, in males, excluding prior other cancers and HO prostate cancer
logicDescription: Primary prostate cancer at first diagnosis, males only, excluding prior cancer (except non-melanoma skin cancer) and excluding h/o prostate cancer and secondary malignant neoplasm of trunk. Malignant tumor of prostate incident cohort: First occurrence of referent concept + descendants excluding secondary cancers, in males, excluding prior other cancers and H/O prostate cancer with >=365d prior observation

Prostate Cancer Parlett (2019) 1+ codes not more than 28 days after a prostate biopsy + Testosterone Users
